watersider
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:A dockside worker.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:New Zealand & Australia
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: also called (informally) wharfie, watersider a wharf cargo worker. Internet search Feb 2006: no spread to other Englishes.
